To run openttd you need data files provided by the original Transport
Tychoon Deluxe.

The following files should be copied to ${PREFIX}/share/openttd/data/
in order to play:
	
	sample.cat
	trg1r.grf
	trgcr.grf
	trghr.grf
	trgir.grf
	trgtr.grf

===========================================================================
